title: Live coverage of today's high school sports
text: Live coverage of today's high school sports We'll be updating the Brockton-Marshfield girls volleyball game on Wednesday afternoon. While you're waiting, check out the jersey ceremony for Marshfield High star Danny Dalton. Comment Posted Sep. 30, 2015 at 12:16 pm Updated at 3:22 PM Penn State-bound Danny Dalton of Marshfield High receives his jersey for the 2016 Semper Fidelis All-American Bowl.
